Symbol.Script_3D:
! Design Table 05.gsm
IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW OFF IF gs_shadow=1 THEN SHADOW ON
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN END IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE THEN gs_resol = 4
mag=zzyzx kmag=mag/24
PEN gs_cont_pen
!****Tabletop MATERIAL gs_topedge_mat ADDZ mag-kmag
RESOL 3*gs_resol CUTPOLYA 2,1,0, 0,0,979, a/2-kmag/2,360,4079
CYLIND kmag,a/2
CUTEND
MATERIAL gs_top_mat CYLIND kmag,a/2-kmag/2
ADDZ -kmag CYLIND kmag,a/2-kmag
ADDZ -kmag CYLIND kmag,a/2-2*kmag DEL 3
RESOL gs_resol !****Legs ADDZ kmag*2 FOR z=1 TO 4 ADDX A/2-4*kmag MATERIAL gs_topedge_mat ELLIPS kmag/2, kmag/2
MATERIAL gs_leg_mat ADDY kmag CYLIND 18*kmag, kmag/2 gosub 11 ADDZ 18*kmag
MATERIAL gs_topedge_mat CYLIND kmag, kmag/2 DEL 1
MATERIAL gs_leg_mat ADDY -kmag*2 CYLIND 18*kmag, kmag/2 gosub 11 ADDZ 18*kmag MATERIAL gs_topedge_mat CYLIND kmag, kmag/2 DEL 4 MATERIAL gs_top_mat
ROTZ 90 NEXT z DEL 5 RESOL 3*gs_resol CYLIND kmag,a/2
ADDZ kmag CYLIND kmag/2,a/2-kmag/2
ADDZ kmag/2 CYLIND kmag/2,a/2-kmag DEL 2
End
11: roty 90 gosub 20 del 1 return
20:
vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1
coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4
base
body -1 return
Symbol.Script_2D:
!! Design Table 05.gsm
unID=1 PEN gs_cont_pen
!!! ********************** Hotspots
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, temp_RR, 1+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, temp_RR, 3+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 temp_RR, 0, unID, temp_RR, 2, A: unID=unID+1
ROT2 90 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, temp_RR, 1+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, temp_RR, 3+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 temp_RR, 0, unID, temp_RR, 2, A: unID=unID+1 DEL 1
ROT2 180 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, temp_RR, 1+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, temp_RR, 3+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 temp_RR, 0, unID, temp_RR, 2, A: unID=unID+1 DEL 1
ROT2 270 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, temp_RR, 1+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, temp_RR, 3+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 temp_RR, 0, unID, temp_RR, 2, A: unID=unID+1 DEL 1
!!! ********************** Minimal Space
call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 7, unID = 3000
!!! ********************** 2D Symbol
SET FILL gs_fill_type POLY2_b 2, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0,901, a/2,360,4001
IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN POLY2_A 2, 1+4,gs_fill_pen, 0,0,901, a/2,360,4001 ENDIF
HOTARC2 0,0,A/2,0,180 HOTARC2 0,0,A/2,180,360
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
d=gs_topedge_mat
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` VALUES "gs_resol" RANGE [3,)
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=4 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol" IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" THEN PARAMETERS B=A IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" THEN PARAMETERS A=B
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" THEN PARAMETERS temp_RR=A/2 IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "temp_RR" THEN PARAMETERS A=temp_RR*2
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" THEN PARAMETERS temp_RR=B/2 IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "temp_RR" THEN PARAMETERS B=temp_RR*2
!!! ******************************** Minimal Space
VALUES "MSFront" RANGE [0,)
